8
00:00:29,096 --> 00:00:32,032
Look, it's not my fault a bunch of guys in sandals did my homework for me

9
00:00:32,033 --> 00:00:33,233
four thousand years ago

10
00:00:36,303 --> 00:00:36,650
That's mine

11
00:00:36,703 --> 00:00:37,604
Ehhh...

12
00:00:39,506 --> 00:00:41,975
