16
00:00:52,039 --> 00:00:53,854
That's...the wonder of me!

17
00:00:55,222 --> 00:00:58,025
No, that's not the wonder of you!
That's the trouble with you!

18
00:00:58,258 --> 00:01:02,563
See, you're always skating by...and someday -- SOMEDAY -- you're gonna hit a rough spot

19
00:01:02,629 --> 00:01:05,899
Who poured you a double mocha of grumpy this morning?

20
00:01:07,534 --> 00:01:09,203
Grumpy

21
00:01:10,370 --> 00:01:14,341
I spent all night on this, I've got a test in structures,
we have to be at work at three, and..

22
00:01:14,708 --> 00:01:19,746
Oh, boy...

23
00:01:16,009 --> 00:01:17,978
I'm breaking up with Melissa today

24
00:01:20,981 --> 00:01:22,249
we have to be at work at three?

25
00:01:25,986 --> 00:01:28,021
